<title>站在房贷利率高位下不来的那群人</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E7%AB%99%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%BF%E8%B4%B7%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%82%A3%E7%BE%A4%E4%BA%BA</link>
